title: Dear Future Wife
actors: Jeovanie Andre, William Alexander, Webbie Casseus, Courtney Garrett
plot: Fellas, have you ever met a woman who has made you think to yourself "Hmmm... This might be the one?" Well, meet Brandon, your local security guard who is a bit awkward when it comes to conversing with females. Anyways, follow him on his journey to finding himself a wife.
